name: 20 Years of SF Dance Music Paul Leath Audio NFT
description: Nearly everyone who has regularly gone out in San Francisco over the last twenty years has seen, heard, and been moved by waves of change in some ways very different from all the others that came before. 5 top SF DJs and Musicians are combining forces for a collective ensemble release with DIGIFIZZY. Taking those tunes to the digi base. Paul Leath has taken on several roles with his involvement in the electronic community, promoter, agent, manager and record distribution. During this entire span, always producing and deejaying.
